## Pagination

Some commands return paginated results. Use `--no-paginate` to get everything at once, or handle pagination properly in scripts.

```bash
# Get all EC2 instances regardless of count
aws ec2 describe-instances --no-paginate

# Manual pagination with next token
aws ec2 describe-instances --max-items 10
# Response includes "NextToken" — pass it to get the next page
aws ec2 describe-instances --max-items 10 --starting-token <NextToken>
```

